OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A mother and stepfather who kept their 
OL,6, starving autistic son locked in "abject
OL,7, squalor and filth" in an attic for     
OL,8, seven months have been jailed.         
OL,10,FMatthew Langley, 22, weighed just 6st  
OL,11,F2lbs (39kg) and was "days away from    
OL,12,Fdeath when he was found in June 2020.  
OL,14,FLorna Hewitt, 43, and husband Craig    
OL,15,FHewitt, 42, were found guilty of false 
OL,16,Fimprisonment by keeping him captive at 
OL,17,Ftheir Sheffield home.                  
OL,19,FThe pair, of Walkley Road, were        
OL,20,Fsentenced to six years in prison.      
